</taxonomicName>
), 
<bibRefCitation id="4B114B37FF880168EE5D6D0EE4920040" author="Benedi, C." box="[595,751,1886,1912]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="286 - 297" refId="ref26549" refString="Benedi, C. (1997) Chamaesyce Gray In: Castroviejo, S., Aedo, C., Benedi, C., Lainz, M., Munoz Garmendia, F., Nieto Feliner, G. &amp; Paiva, J. (Eds.) Flora Iberica vol. 8. Real Jardin Botanico-CSIC, Madrid, pp. 286 - 297." type="book chapter" year="1997">Benedì (1997</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 69, under the name 
<taxonomicName id="E8804D45FF880168E8016D0EE3710040" box="[1039,1292,1886,1912]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Chamaesyce" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maculata">
<emphasis id="1DF4EAD4FF880168E8016D0EE3710040" box="[1039,1292,1886,1912]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Chamaesyce maculata</emphasis>
